{
  "title": "Glassy-Jelly Uruguayan Oats Bake",
  "description": "Sweet and festive, this glassy-jelly Uruguayan oats bake features katsuramuki-cut oats and is ayurvedic-tamasic-friendly. Perfect for a special occasions or holiday gatherings.",
  "cuisine": "Uruguayan",
